        <summary type="html"><![CDATA[Welcome to Prismatica — a polymorphic data platform built as part of the ft_transcendence project at 42.]]></summary>
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>Welcome to <strong>Prismatica</strong> — a polymorphic data platform built as part of the ft_transcendence project at 42.</p>
<h2 class="anchor anchorTargetStickyNavbar_Vzrq" id="what-is-prismatica">What is Prismatica?<a href="https://univers42.github.io/blog/welcome#what-is-prismatica" class="hash-link" aria-label="Direct link to What is Prismatica?" title="Direct link to What is Prismatica?" translate="no">​</a></h2>
<p>Prismatica is a modern full-stack platform featuring:</p>
<ul>
<li class=""><strong>Dual-Database Architecture</strong> — PostgreSQL 16 for relational data, MongoDB 7 for flexible documents</li>
<li class=""><strong>REST API</strong> with Express and schema-validated endpoints</li>
<li class=""><strong>React 19 + Vite 6</strong> frontend with TypeScript</li>
<li class=""><strong>Docker Compose</strong> orchestration for development and production</li>
<li class=""><strong>ABAC Security</strong> — Attribute-Based Access Control at every layer</li>
<li class=""><strong>NestJS Backend</strong> with Prisma ORM</li>
</ul>
<h2 class="anchor anchorTargetStickyNavbar_Vzrq" id="documentation">Documentation<a href="https://univers42.github.io/blog/welcome#documentation" class="hash-link" aria-label="Direct link to Documentation" title="Direct link to Documentation" translate="no">​</a></h2>
<p>Explore the full documentation to get started:</p>
<ul>
<li class=""><a class="" href="https://univers42.github.io/docs/intro">Introduction</a> — Overview and quick start</li>
<li class=""><a class="" href="https://univers42.github.io/docs/architecture">Architecture</a> — System design and data flow</li>
<li class=""><a class="" href="https://univers42.github.io/docs/setup">Setup Guide</a> — Local development setup</li>
<li class=""><a class="" href="https://univers42.github.io/docs/api">API Reference</a> — Endpoint documentation</li>
</ul>
<h2 class="anchor anchorTargetStickyNavbar_Vzrq" id="get-involved">Get Involved<a href="https://univers42.github.io/blog/welcome#get-involved" class="hash-link" aria-label="Direct link to Get Involved" title="Direct link to Get Involved" translate="no">​</a></h2>
<p>Prismatica is open source. Check out the <a class="" href="https://univers42.github.io/docs/contributing">Contributing Guide</a> and the <a href="https://github.com/Univers42/ft_transcendence" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="">GitHub repository</a>.</p>]]></content>
